reviews.review_text: Impressive VHS? VCR??!! Bang up job to the collaborated efforts of WPYX and the star duo: Rich P. and Mr. Keo. Historic run with a quality download thanks to yee. The Knick was (and remains) a superb venue with great acoustics and they rocked it for all its worth!
Holy Sound Quality, Batman!! All systems are go for this upload!  Wow!!!!!
